snippet.title: Cast-n-Blast gameplay
snippet.description:
A gameplay video of the game Cast-n-Blast, which I made in 1.5 months with Game Maker Studio 2.

This game is a top-down arena shooter about a mage, who fights different foes in the arena.

Download - https://tricky-fat-cat.itch.io/cast-n-blast
